Lease options available:
Lease through June 30, 2025, at $2,100 per month until June 30, 2024 and $2,200 per month from July 1, 2024, to June 30 2025
OR
Lease through June 30, 2024, at $2,200 per month.
Tenant pays all utilities.
Up to 2 pets allowed under 30 lbs or 1 pet allowed for dogs over 30 lbs.
Per pet, an additional $300 refundable deposit and $35/month pet fee
Gas forced air heat and A/C window unit(s).
Available immediately for showings and move-in. Property can be held with negotiation.

Step into this charming home nestled in the Washington Virginia Vale neighborhood! This 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom half duplex, built in 1957 and spanning 1650 square feet, has been thoughtfully modernized. The kitchen is a showstopper, boasting lavish quartz counters and top-of-the-line appliances. Gleaming hardwood floors adorn the spacious living room, suffused with natural light that creates an irresistible ambiance.
Outside, discover a fully fenced backyard, a private sanctuary featuring a sprawling brick patio and ample space for gardening or hosting delightful backyard gatherings. The sizable unfinished basement offers private laundry facilities and abundant space perfect for a home gym, office setup, and abundant storage solutions!
Conveniently located near Garland Park and Cherry Creek Trail, this property offers easy access to Colorado Blvd and i-25, making commuting a breeze. It's situated close to George Washington High School and a grocery store, ensuring all necessities are within reach. Experience the perfect blend of modernized comfort and an inviting atmosphere in this home, with the added bonus of a fantastic neighborhood and amenities just moments away.

This unit offers reduced upfront costs with Rhino. Ask us how you can save cash on the deposit requirements when you move in. If you opt out of this program our standard deposit is equivalent to one full month of rent.

Other terms, fees, and conditions may apply. MOD Properties cannot verify the accuracy of property information listed on third party sites. Please visit MOD Properties website to confirm property information. The required resident benefit package is $32/month. All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed and is subject to change. Rent is subject to change.

Applicant has the right to provide MOD Properties with a Portable Tenant Screening Report (PTSR) that is not more than 30 days old, as defined in 38-12-902(2.5), Colorado Revised Statutes; and 2) if Applicant provides MOD Properties with a PTSR, MOD Properties is prohibited from: a) charging Applicant a rental application fee; or b) charging Applicant a fee for MOD Properties to access or use the PTSR.

Offered by MOD Properties.
